---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AuthorProfile from '../components/AuthorProfile.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about the author and purpose of this digital garden"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 prose prose-invert lg:prose-xl">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h1>About the Author</h1>
      <AuthorProfile showExtended={true} />
    </div>

    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2>Welcome to My Digital Garden</h2>
      <p>
        This space serves as a personal knowledge repository where I document my journey 
        through software development, system design, and technical exploration. Unlike 
        traditional blogs, this digital garden grows organically, with content that evolves 
        and matures over time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-xl mb-12">
      <h2 class="mt-0">Areas of Focus</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Technical Expertise</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Software Architecture & System Design</li>
            <li>Web Development & Modern Frameworks</li>
            <li>Performance Optimization</li>
            <li>DevOps & Cloud Infrastructure</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Content Categories</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>In-depth Technical Guides</li>
            <li>Best Practices & Patterns</li>
            <li>Tool Comparisons & Reviews</li>
            <li>Industry Insights</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2>Writing Philosophy</h2>
      <p>
        Each article aims to provide clear, practical insights backed by real-world 
        experience. The content here evolves alongside my professional journey, 
        reflecting new learnings and changing perspectives in the tech landscape.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Focus on practical, actionable knowledge</li>
        <li>Regular updates to keep content relevant</li>
        <li>Clear examples and detailed explanations</li>
        <li>Open to feedback and discussions</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="mt-0">Stay Connected</h2>
      <p>
        Keep up with the latest content and updates:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Subscribe to the RSS feed for new articles</li>
        <li>Follow the blog's social media channels</li>
        <li>Join the discussion in article comments</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .card {
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.7) 0%,
      rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.6) 100%
    );
    border: 1px solid rgba(75, 85, 99, 0.3);
  }

  .prose h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    color: #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 1.875rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .prose ul {
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }

  .prose strong {
    color: #f1f5f9;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .prose h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .prose h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>